STATE of North Carolina
v.
William Jesse BUCHANAN No. 305P17 Supreme Court of North Carolina. December 7, 2017 Ronald D. Williams, II, Assistant Attorney General. William Jesse Buchanan, for Buchanan, William Jesse. Robert S. Banks, District Attorney, for State of North Carolina.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the application filed by Defendant on the 27th of November 2017 in this matter for Writ of Habeas Corpus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Yancey County:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 7th of December 2017."
